---
title:  Turkey Fajita Bowls with Pico de Gallo, Chili-Lime Crema & Tortilla Chips
description: For this fajita-inspired meal, our chefs thought outside the box—errr, tortilla—to create some seriously epic bowls. You’ll start with a base of buttery rice, saucy spiced turkey, and sautéed peppers and onions, then jazz things up with Monterey Jack cheese, homemade pico de gallo, chili lime crema, and blue corn tortilla chips. When ready to build your bowl, feel free to go wild with assembly. Crema on bottom! Rice on top of turkey! Crush up your tortilla chips for a crunchy garnish, or serve along the side for scooping—that’s the beauty of making it yourself!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/678ec2638cb13d95928276b4-3febe2b0.jpeg
